name: Transition point
query:
SELECT tr.description, t.type, p.description as program, c.major_primary, c.major_secondary
FROM transition_points t inner join curriculums c on t.curriculum_id = c.id
inner join programs p on c.program_id = p.id
inner join terms tr on t.term_id = tr.id

---
:parameters: !ruby/hash:ActiveSupport::HashWithIndifferentAccess
  name1: description
  type1: text_field
  default1: description
  label1: description
  active1: 0
  name2: type
  type2: select
  default2: type
  label2: type
  active2: 1
  name3: program
  type3: program_select
  default3: program
  label3: program
  active3: 1
  name4: major_primary
  type4: text_field
  default4: major_primary
  label4: major_primary
  active4: 1
  name5: major_secondary
  type5: text_field
  default5: major_secondary
  label5: major_secondary
  active5: 0
  length: 5
